{"tid":684301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最後一支茶字典","createTime":"2018-05-30T12:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T12:34:01.000Z","uid":76526,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec924d2da259231cca433d659ad45159618591f2","tid":684301,"uid":76526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩落樓下士多買野飲，突然間好想飲茶字典，於是叫老闆畀一支我，佢同我講呢支茶字典係佢間鋪最後一支，維他唔再出產茶字典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前細個每次落街玩，踢波，都會帶四蚊買茶字典飲，係小學至中學飲得最多既野飲，有時冇帶錢問朋友借黎飲一啖已經覺得好滿足，最鐘意係蜜桃味同冰極檸檬味，後尾大個左開始少飲左，幾乎冇飲，估唔到今日突然想飲翻竟然係最後一支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/200408_c792e2ba589d8af4c2ef0738cd07d564.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F200408_c792e2ba589d8af4c2ef0738cd07d564.png&h=cd27ae9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85122c28aec832389a4119e5a92f6e75578410bd","tid":684301,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b2ef5f5ff3d0fbf1b08fa8fde9f587e60cd9332","tid":684301,"uid":2776,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:12:32.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 阿波羅大撚把"},{"pid":"a9b0205c8ee74c31a3812b7c274e0df7593b1e9b","tid":684301,"uid":76526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b2ef5f5ff3d0fbf1b08fa8fde9f587e60cd9332","tid":684301,"uid":2776,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:12:32.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 阿波羅大撚把"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"停產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aec36eaf0cdd813f3bbd7998de73333fd191ec4","tid":684301,"uid":2776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9b0205c8ee74c31a3812b7c274e0df7593b1e9b","tid":684301,"uid":76526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b2ef5f5ff3d0fbf1b08fa8fde9f587e60cd9332","